OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud in places will
OL,6,Fsoon clear with sunshine to follow but
OL,7,Fturning to hazy sunshine in the
OL,8,Fafternoon as high cloud moves across.
OL,9,FFeeling warm with light winds for most.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mild night for many with
OL,12,Fhigh cloud clearing to give clear
OL,13,Fspells later on. Cooler in rural areas
OL,14,Fwith fog patches developing in places
OL,15,Fwith the wind remaining light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA warm or very warm day with
OL,18,Fplenty of sunshine for most with the
OL,19,Fwind remaining light. Feeling a little
OL,20,Fcooler along the coast with the sea
OL,21,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
