OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fand very warm or hot for most on
OL,7,FMonday. Expecting temperatures to
OL,8,Fdecrease Tuesday and Wednesday but
OL,9,Fremaining above average for the time
OL,10,Fof year.
